ed a backing band that features a bevy of heavyweight jazz artists including acclaimed pianist robert glasper saxophonist ron blake trumpeter ravi best and others however rather than having james focus on jazz standards or even jazzinfluenced pop songs wamble helped the vocalist craft an rbinflected album that brings to mind classic artists like carole king and hall  oates as well as more contemporary singers including beyoncï¿½ and the late amy winehouse james who made her broadway debut in  alongside nathan lane in the addams family has a big resonant voice with a ton of flexibility perfectly suited for such crisp soulful cuts as heart shake and bring yourself to me elsewhere she delves into several equally compelling bluesy midtempo numbers including you never lied and drown ultimately its that voice  matched with wambles superb musical vision  that creates the soulful exuberant vibe of hunter  matt collarpersonnel morgan james vocals background vocals recording information brooklyn recording brooklyn ny engine room audio new york ny geddough studios harmlem ny quad studios new york ny the samurai hotel new york nyÂ Â Â see full description morgan james  hunter album track listing trksongtimeÂ priceÂ buy mp call my nameÂ mp available ondifferent album huntermp available ondifferent album heart shakemp available ondifferent album bring yourself to memp available ondifferent album i want yoump available ondifferent album i dont speak yoump available ondifferent album you never liedmp available ondifferent album say the wordsmp available ondifferent album sweetest sound theÂ  drownmp available ondifferent album fed up on yoump available ondifferent album shes gonemp available ondifferent album dancing in the darkÂ mp available ondifferent album let me keep youwith robert glaspermp available ondifferent album hunter songs customer reviews average rating   good mix of blues and jazzlittle bits of every thingblues jazz and uptempobyÂ scott arizonaÂ  have you heard this